item.title: 【Live Audios (lossy)】MP3 - Beyoncé - The Mrs. Carter Show World Tour: Rock In Rio
item.description:
Estou disponibilizando a minha versão da apresentação da Beyoncé no Rock In Rio de 2013, porque como o áudio que foi transmitido pelo canal Multishow estava com baixa resolução, e a versão que foi transmitido na Globo tá bem melhor, sendo que com cortes, resolvi fazer em um só, incluindo as partes que faltavam num show apenas, a única música que não foi transmitida pela Globo foi "Get Me Bodied", mas isso é o de menos. Aproveitem, e depois, se puderem, me digam como ficou.

I'm making my version of Beyoncé's performance at Rock In Rio 2013 available, because as the audio that was broadcast on the Multishow channel was in low resolution, and the version that was broadcast on Globo is much better, with cuts, I decided to make in one, including the parts that were missing from just one show, the only song that wasn't broadcast on Globo was "Get Me Bodied", but that's the least of it. Enjoy, and then, if you can, tell me how it turned out.

item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - Utada Hikaru - Science Fiction (FLAC 24bits/96kHz) [2024]
item.description:
SCIENCE FICTION is the first best album released by Utada Hikaru. It was released in two versions: a limited CD+Booklet edition and a regular CD edition. The limited edition has a linticular cover, which changes the colors of the image at different angles. The album is a joint venture release by Epic Records Japan (CD) and Universal Music Japan (Digital).
